name: Health Food
description:
Help Healthy Mouth eat health food to gain points, and get healthier!

Health Food is a retro style arcade game with a healthy eco-friendly message to it. The game starts out slowly, but progressively speeds up as Healthy Mouth gets healthier. Your game play will last, and your score will get higher as long as you don't eat too many cheeseburgers!

If you, or a loved one enjoy the retro style game play of the late 70's, and early 80's then Health Food is the game for you!
